## Conclusion

Overall the prototype was received very positively by all 5 test users. The AI-driven personalization through MoodSync AI was highlighted as the standout feature. Users found the app intuitive, calming, and well-designed. All 5 compulsory features — Stress Tracking Dashboard, MoodSync AI, Pod Scheduler, Breathe With Me, and Post-Session Journal — were successfully understood and used by all test users without difficulty.
